a capability we call personalized tuning. We demonstrate through a variety of 
applications written on top of CarMA that personalized tuning can result in 
over 10% gains in fuel efficiency. We achieve this through route-specific or 
driver-specific customizations. Furthermore, CarMA is capable of improving user 
