 1 to 1000 MB. This level of diversity suggests that mechanisms 
 to improve user experience or energy consumption will 
 be more effective if they learn and adapt to user behavior. 
 We find that qualitative similarities exist among users that 
 facilitate the task of learning user behavior. For instance, 
