 radios. Our Tenet software runs application code on the higher-tier 
 nodes, and provides a generic interface for tasking sensors and 
 actuators. This separation of functionality simplifies application 
 development greatly, since developers can reuse networking and sensor 
 data extraction code, thereby reducing application development time. 
 We will report on the development of and experiences with 
 structural data acquisition application for a long-span suspension 
 bridge using Tenet. We will report on our experiences in deploying 
